{"tid":1311553,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"劉曉波留畀我哋嘅提醒","createTime":"2019-07-13T09:02:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T04:54:30.000Z","uid":160637,"like":230,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"3d1bb1aa2e20d9be3f0bc5cb787e4e484d351786","tid":1311553,"uid":160637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T09:02:56.000Z","msg":"這是他的最後陳述：「因為，仇恨會腐蝕一個人的智慧和良知，敵人意識將毒化一個民族的精神，煽動起你死我活的殘酷鬥爭，毀掉一個社會的寬容和人性，阻礙一個國家走向自由民主的進程。」"},{"pid":"d81664c275667a278dffab90563d72bf2e74bd27","tid":1311553,"uid":4050,"like":33,"dislike":3,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T09:04:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>［抗分化］共匪宜家玩緊老技倆，拉一派打一派</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n共匪一貫手法，分化、滲透，然後拉籠一派打一派，政府有時會軟硬兼施，打下感情牌博同情，亦會派三毛做打手，屌/笑/鬧/玩膠嗰啲當然90%都係三毛，但亦都唔排除有真心膠中計信咗佢地一套，所謂拉一派打一派，群眾鬥群眾就係咁，要你自相殘殺，孤立主要敵人，然後共匪就可以輕鬆逐個擊破，2014年雨革因示威者內部分裂而亡，切記歷史教訓，無論如何都唔可以比三毛成功分化"},{"pid":"34732aa61d9867719e1e40764338da61bba9b081","tid":1311553,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T09:14:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"00d1676e8efec9f795d102160cdfb593458fc9aa","tid":1311553,"uid":160637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:55:04.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"e09fdbebcca7794c230d40340f36a830d8a37166","tid":1311553,"uid":160637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T17:29:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"647ffd4cb0c5ee2d0dff2d359879d3fc354725a9","tid":1311553,"uid":195252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T19:27:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ea5761658cf329a4e522d49ec7e9ed4ced15813","tid":1311553,"uid":266503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T19:28:59.000Z","msg":"槍響之前：金恩博士與三個邪惡的最後鬥爭<br />\n人們當然知道馬丁路德金恩博士為黑人民權運動奮鬥，知道他著名的演說「我有一個夢」，或者知道他在整整五十年前的1968年被槍殺。<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@soundfury/%E6%A7%8D%E9%9F%BF%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D-%E9%87%91%E6%81%A9%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E8%88%87%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8B%E9%82%AA%E6%83%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E9%AC%A5%E7%88%AD-c3dd35a3dcf4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40soundfury%2F%25E6%25A7%258D%25E9%259F%25BF%25E4%25B9%258B%25E5%2589%258D-%25E9%2587%2591%25E6%2581%25A9%25E5%258D%259A%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E8%2588%2587%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%2580%258B%25E9%2582%25AA%25E6%2583%25A1%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BE%258C%25E9%25AC%25A5%25E7%2588%25AD-c3dd35a3dcf4&d=ev%2BvVaAtQ3cORw7W3wlzWb7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=16e0c534\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@soundfury/%E6%A7%8D%E9%9F%BF%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D-%E9%87%91%E6%81%A9%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E8%88%87%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8B%E9%82%AA%E6%83%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E9%AC%A5%E7%88%AD-c3dd35a3dcf4</a><br />\n泛民，要學馬丁路德金。<br />\n我不反對不支持勇武，但理解。請在勇武前冷靜想清楚後果(自己和旁人）.不受傷，不流血。<br />\n「我有一個夢」背後有「選票與子彈」支持同保護<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/選票還是子彈\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E9%81%B8%E7%A5%A8%E9%82%84%E6%98%AF%E5%AD%90%E5%BD%88&d=ev%2BvVaAtQ3cORw7W3wlzWb7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=725afc06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/選票還是子彈</a><br />\n或先岩 更正"},{"pid":"f077525f5ce0d61e2880384366a3eee95581f5b4","tid":1311553,"uid":160637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T02:59:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">推</span>"},{"pid":"1731e622254ed796bdc56f7ea22283e6fb823cda","tid":1311553,"uid":160637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:25:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0d6c8e8c0091cd0140721c562838ef7dd240ae2","tid":1311553,"uid":160637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:51:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">推</span>"},{"pid":"088aae6d875c7cc52834c8e688121d5b06b22007","tid":1311553,"uid":273284,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3d1bb1aa2e20d9be3f0bc5cb787e4e484d351786","